Is Saido Berahino the latest star on Manchester United's summer shopping list?

Louis van Gaal will embark upon a huge summer spending spree this summer as he looks to fire United back to the top of English and European football.

And West Bromwich Albion striker Berahino has got tongues wagging that he features on United's wishlist after attending the FA Cup clash against Arsenal.

